37 annual Afterschool Day at the state capitol to encourage lawmakers to recognize the critical
38 role afterschool programs play in preparing Georgia's youth for success in college, career,
39 and life.
40 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
41 the members of this body recognize February 12, 2025, as Afterschool Day at the state
42 capitol.
43 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
44 and directed to make a copy of this resolution available for distribution to the Georgia
45 Statewide Afterschool Network.
